<l>allavai tēya vaṟamperuku nallavai</l>
<l>nāṭi yiṉiya coliṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>His merit waxes while demerit wanes, if seeking</l>
<l>what is useful, he says what is sweet.</l>
